sql_query: SELECT      s.STORE_NUM_NAME,     s.CITY,     s.STATE,     SUM(CAST(s.DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2))) as TOTAL_SALES FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES s GROUP BY      s.STORE_NUM_NAME,     s.CITY,     s.STATE ORDER BY TOTAL_SALES DESC LIMIT 2
